Package lubiku.castleQuest.Configuration.Configurators

Interface Configurator

All Known Implementing Classes:
ApplicationWindowManager, GameWindowManager, HeroManager, MapManager, MonsterManager, NPCManager, ObjectManager
public interface Configurator

Configurator

The Configurator interface defines methods for configuring objects using JSON data. Classes implementing this interface can provide custom logic to handle the configuration based on their specific requirements.
